r accident charge, we have you covered.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.manninglaw.com\/federal-crimes-raleigh\/\"><strong>Federal Crime Defense<\/strong><\/a><br \/>Federal crimes are a serious matter and should be treated as such. Manning Law Firm, has experience working with clients charged with everything from bank robbery to drug trafficking.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h3>Why Choose Us?<\/h3>\n<p>Manning Law Firm has the experience you need when it comes to your case. We work tirelessly to defend you, and always take the time to understand your case inside and out.<\/p>\n<p>We will begin working on your case immediately, and will leave no detail uncovered until you have the best possible outcome. With more than 40 years of experience working with the justice system, we know the ins and outs of every law, and how to navigate through them.<\/p>\n<p>Not only have our clients in Raleigh and surrounding areas trusted us with their cases, but we have also received recognition from our peers as one of the best criminal defense attorneys, year after year.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/contact\/\" class=\"body-cta\">The bottom line is that Manning Law Firm has the willingness and the experience to defend you when you need it. Contact us today to get started.<\/a><br \/><div class=\"divider\"><\/div><\/p>\n<h4>Meet Our Attorneys<\/h4>\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Tommy-Manning-c-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" class=\"wp-image-1472 size-medium alignleft\" srcset=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Tommy-Manning-c-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Tommy-Manning-c.jpg 256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" \/>\n<h5><a href=\"https:\/\/www.manninglaw.com\/criminal-attorneys-raleigh\/thomas-c-manning\/\">Thomas C. Manning<\/a><\/h5>\n<p>Thomas C. Manning is a Board-Certified Specialist in State and Federal Criminal Law. For more than 40 years, he has tried cases in State and Federal Courts. As a former Federal law clerk and prosecutor, he has a depth of experience and breadth of knowledge in criminal law cases of all types, and jury trial experience second to none in North Carolina. He carries the highest peer-review rating of competence and ethics, and is listed in many peer-rated publications as a top lawyer.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\n<p><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignleft size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"256\" height=\"320\" src=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Taylor-Manning-c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1460\" style=\"aspect-ratio:0.8;width:241px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Taylor-Manning-c.jpg 256w, https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/MLF-Taylor-Manning-c-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.manninglaw.com\/criminal-attorneys-raleigh\/t-taylor-manning\/\">T. Taylor Manning<\/a><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Taylor joined his father in 2011 following several years of practice with a well-respected law firm in eastern North Carolina. There, he gained valuable experience in family law litigation, minor criminal trials, and a wide variety of other litigated matters. Since practicing in the Triangle area, he has accumulated expertise and experience in a large number of criminal law matters, including District Court DWI and traffic matters, misdemeanor and felony drug cases, and Superior Court jury trial experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignleft size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/wp-conten